Dialogue: 1,0:22:28.37,0:22:34.04,Songs,,0,0,35,,{\an8\blur0.6}I want to see you once a thousand nights have passed
Dialogue: 1,0:22:35.00,0:22:38.21,Songs,,0,0,35,,{\an8\blur0.6}I dreamt I was flying through the night sky
Dialogue: 1,0:22:38.21,0:22:41.09,Songs,,0,0,35,,{\an8\blur0.6}On a magic carpet
