Dialogue: 1,0:23:22.76,0:23:28.97,Songs,,0,0,35,,{\an8\blur0.6}Even though I could just type a <3 and send it to you
Dialogue: 1,0:23:29.22,0:23:34.77,Songs,,0,0,35,,{\an8\blur0.6}It's hard to sum up the way I feel for you
