Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.83,0:01:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So emerald green is in this season, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.58,0:01:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Jessica is a reader model?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.05,0:01:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Jessica really is the trendiest girl in town!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.09,0:01:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.26,0:01:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Jessica!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.60,0:01:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Cony!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.91,0:01:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Go clothes shopping again?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.67,0:02:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! I got lots of new outfits.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.64,0:02:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You like?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.57,0:02:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.93,0:02:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Gorgeous!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.03,0:02:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got a real good eye for fashion, Jessica!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.16,0:02:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, it's all just cheap knockoffs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.28,0:02:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.08,0:02:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You look stylish in just about anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.37,0:02:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.04,0:02:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Just look at this dress!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.32,0:02:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fabulous!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.04,0:02:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that one's branded,\Nso it's a bit expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.84,0:02:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.17,0:02:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It totally wouldn't look good on me anyways.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.22,0:02:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.76,0:02:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, it won't fit me at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.85,0:02:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It would!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.68,0:02:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Really? Can I try it on then?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.81,0:02:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Please? Please? Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.76,0:02:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.31,0:02:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay, I get to try it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.90,0:02:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'll go make some tea!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.03,0:02:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's a bit tight...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.97,0:03:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,See! It looks great on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.00,0:03:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You look totes pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.75,0:03:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.79,0:03:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm totes feeling it too now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.25,0:03:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It fits you perfectly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.73,0:03:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It does, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.99,0:03:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cuz, thing is, I have to ask you a favor...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.30,0:03:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.43,0:03:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you lend me this dress for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.64,0:03:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.48,0:03:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,J-Just for a day!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.84,0:03:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But I just bought it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.10,0:03:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't even worn it myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.86,0:03:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.77,0:03:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Why though?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.56,0:03:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I... It's just... Y'know, girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.19,0:03:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going on a date today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.20,0:03:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So I wanted to wear something extra purty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.87,0:03:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A date? With who?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.03,0:03:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, just some guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.62,0:03:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No biggie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.83,0:03:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, pretty please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.33,0:03:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,With a cherry on top!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.43,0:03:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with the weird poses?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.19,0:03:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, I'm just...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.19,0:03:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...doing the "pretty please" hula dance pose!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.80,0:03:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Never heard of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.84,0:03:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Aloha 'oe...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.76,0:04:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty please, for'e...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.76,0:04:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me borrow this dress...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.76,0:04:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.27,0:04:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Cony?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.53,0:04:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I managed to throw her off...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.69,0:04:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I just have to fix it up before she notices.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.70,0:04:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Wah-lah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.95,0:04:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Darn, I made one of the sleeves shorter...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.08,0:04:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I just have to match it on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.00,0:04:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Bam, all done!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.25,0:04:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.80,0:04:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A bit over here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.38,0:04:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.93,0:04:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I made it sleeveless!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.47,0:04:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Put some of the cloth over here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.41,0:04:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A bit of this and that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Stitch it all together...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.35,0:04:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm done!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.69,0:04:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's supposed to wear a dress this small?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.07,0:05:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, shoot! I forgot I asked Moon to come over!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.08,0:05:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Cony? Cony!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.59,0:05:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The heck? Is she gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.95,0:05:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,After asking me to come help you\Nset up your new computer, no less!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.38,0:05:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What do I do with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.35,0:05:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.68,0:05:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have the large—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.18,0:05:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, the normal size of this dress?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.81,0:05:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, I'm afraid we sold out of that earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.07,0:05:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,850)}Whaaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.91,0:05:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Cony!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.58,0:05:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,J-Jessica?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.12,0:05:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Cony?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.04,0:05:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, whash up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.25,0:05:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I was going to ask you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.25,0:06:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to your date?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.55,0:06:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Date? Oh, {\i1}that{\i0} date!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.47,0:06:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to cancel, my teeth randomly started aching.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.55,0:06:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright? Your face is awful swelled up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.02,0:06:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, could be worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.98,0:06:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Well, sorry about the date.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.06,0:06:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Get better soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.42,0:06:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.08,0:06:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If the date is off, I suppose\Nyou don't need that anymore, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.90,0:06:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you return it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.12,0:06:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, my dress!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.04,0:06:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sowwy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.29,0:06:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sowwy, Jessica!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.79,0:06:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.86,0:06:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The dress...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.50,0:06:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Your dress...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.17,0:06:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It was stowen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.55,0:06:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone stole it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.26,0:06:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Some burglar snuck in while I was at the dentist
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.59,0:06:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and they stole it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.22,0:06:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? A burglar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.10,0:06:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.22,0:06:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We better call the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to exaggerate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.85,0:06:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,They didn't steal anything important!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.64,0:07:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What about my dress?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.19,0:07:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I guess that's important, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.19,0:07:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just pay you back for the dress!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.49,0:07:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.16,0:07:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not at fault here,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.04,0:07:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,the criminal is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.99,0:07:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And we can't let society's evils get off scot-free!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.29,0:07:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We better call 911 right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.67,0:07:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,J-Jessica! Please calm down...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.63,0:07:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Cony, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.08,0:07:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Juby-julee...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.92,0:07:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Wait, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.05,0:07:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.59,0:07:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}We have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.84,0:07:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.48,0:07:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.39,0:07:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What's all the fuss about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.24,0:07:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Cony was attacked by a burglar!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.40,0:07:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.48,0:07:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You were attacked?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.73,0:07:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Did they punch you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.88,0:07:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! Your poor little face is all swollen!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.15,0:07:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I never said I got attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.03,0:07:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, I've heard about a gang\Nof thieves making their way around town...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.86,0:07:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That must be it! It's that rotten gang of thieves!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.76,0:07:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hold on, wait a minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.08,0:07:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I know who it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.92,0:07:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:07:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.92,0:08:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.42,0:08:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Saw who?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.51,0:08:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who robbed Cony...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.39,0:08:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,...was Moon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.06,0:08:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.60,0:08:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Moon?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.93,0:08:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed. I saw it with my own two eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.27,0:08:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He was getting very worked up\Nright outside Cony's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.77,0:08:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.65,0:08:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Moon would never...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.72,0:08:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.82,0:08:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Moon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.28,0:08:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,1000)}Brown caught this pic while we were passing by.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.74,0:08:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Moon...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.54,0:08:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a criminal...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.79,0:08:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys, he's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.58,0:08:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Hey, guys, what are y'all up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.46,0:08:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.71,0:08:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Struuum!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.38,0:08:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Struuum!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.13,0:08:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The mandolin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.39,0:08:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your issue, Cony?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.14,0:08:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought we had made plans.\NWhy'd you stand me up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.97,0:08:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just busy with something...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.81,0:09:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, plans?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.06,0:09:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me your date was with Moon?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.19,0:09:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The date?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.40,0:09:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. Nope. Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.86,0:09:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.82,0:09:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a good thing he wasn't your date, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.70,0:09:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Would've been very shocking\Nto get robbed by your boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.33,0:09:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Boyfriend or not, it's still shocking!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.25,0:09:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Our good friend is a burglar!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.33,0:09:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.33,0:09:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Moon, I'm quite shocked, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.40,0:09:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.71,0:09:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.67,0:09:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.34,0:09:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,To the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.63,0:09:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bring you there so you can 'fess up for what you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.43,0:09:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Stealing my dress, duh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.56,0:09:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone knows!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.68,0:09:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You snuck into Cony's room
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.89,0:09:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and stole Jessica's dress!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.02,0:09:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I snuck into Cony's room...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.57,0:09:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, why am I taking {\i1}Jessica's{\i0} thing\Nfrom {\i1}Cony's{\i0} house?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.94,0:09:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Makes no sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.49,0:09:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The point is that you're a rotten thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.84,0:09:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.45,0:09:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We have proof too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.24,0:10:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm, hey, you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.71,0:10:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you might be getting the wrong idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.42,0:10:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh come on, why would I steal your stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.00,0:10:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And even if I did,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.17,0:10:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,why would I take a dress of all things?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.88,0:10:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It all makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.76,0:10:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I told ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.16,0:10:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're into that kinda thing, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.76,0:10:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't mean...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.68,0:10:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, it all adds up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.73,0:10:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you insinuating?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.36,0:10:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,One of you actually called them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.20,0:10:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,End of the line, Moon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.60,0:10:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotta be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.52,0:10:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He's getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.60,0:10:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Freeze, Moon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.92,0:10:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.92,0:10:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all my...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.08,0:10:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,my fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.76,0:10:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.32,0:11:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry I kept this from you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.16,0:11:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You should've just apologized from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.60,0:11:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.80,0:11:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.76,0:11:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I can always buy more clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.44,0:11:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.72,0:11:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll buy some to make up for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.36,0:11:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get a job to raise the money...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.96,0:11:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.80,0:11:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.64,0:11:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I get paid modeling for magazines anyways.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.52,0:11:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got a real big heart, Jessica.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.41,0:11:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,My, but I'm so thin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.20,0:11:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have this, Sally!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.16,0:11:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow! It's just the right size!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.92,0:11:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.28,0:11:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,All's well that ends well!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.64,0:11:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.92,0:11:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's quite alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.24,0:11:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How does it look?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.40,0:11:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.36,0:11:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to Jessica to make\Nthe best fashion choices!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.04,0:11:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.04,0:11:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I forgetting something...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.82,0:11:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Why me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.59,0:12:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Where oh where are you, Red?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since you left me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.14,0:12:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,my life's been in utter shambles...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.31,0:12:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back here, Cony!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.39,0:12:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me back my dango!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.31,0:12:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.02,0:12:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.69,0:12:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If only I could constantly smile\Nthe way Cony does...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.61,0:12:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm so young and promising, and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.57,0:12:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, I'm so ugly...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.37,0:12:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should shave...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.25,0:12:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that went terribly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.67,0:12:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,"Don't forget to buy some eggs?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.67,0:13:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Cony's throwing\Nan omelet rice party at her place today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.81,0:13:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.39,0:13:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.48,0:13:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not enough?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.90,0:13:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No, sir, your change!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.04,0:13:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just awful...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.29,0:13:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,How could all this happen to James,\Nthe spirit of charm, the king of beauty...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.60,0:13:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sally...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.39,0:13:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she knows how I can stop this cycle of misery...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.14,0:13:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Sally—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:13:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No one's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.27,0:13:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Could've sworn someone called me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.16,0:14:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There she goes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.75,0:14:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Open it up, Brown!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.38,0:14:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Would it kill ya to react?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.09,0:14:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What, unless you're frozen from shock?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.35,0:14:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you guys help out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.04,0:14:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Cony, I got a carton of ten eggs...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,James, open this up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.15,0:14:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,A ghost!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.20,0:14:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you two doing...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.83,0:14:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That really knocked the wind out of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.16,0:14:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right. James, the eggs!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.96,0:14:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The eggs are in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.50,0:15:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.21,0:15:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This is supposed to be an omelet and rice party!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.93,0:15:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It got on my Monthly Beauty...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.02,0:15:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Just ketchup and rice isn't too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.04,0:15:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But it would've been even better\Nwith that fluffy yellow goodness on top!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.78,0:15:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And whose fault is that, Moon?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.19,0:15:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you blaming me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.70,0:15:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, James. Eat up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.78,0:15:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your next vacation gonna be?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.16,0:15:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A theme park!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Brown?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.83,0:15:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,An aquarium?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.04,0:15:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Brown, there are no salmon in the aquarium.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.59,0:15:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And you, James?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.17,0:15:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll go to the dump.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.09,0:15:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, the dump?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.97,0:15:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you supposed to do there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.89,0:15:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch as they take care of the trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.89,0:16:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Knowing that eventually I'll be\Ntaken care of just like that trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.44,0:16:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What's all that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.65,0:16:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you waste a vacation\Non something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.70,0:16:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Where would you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.86,0:16:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I dunno, maybe out camping!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.66,0:16:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Camping?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.49,0:16:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You remember that riverbed we went to last summer?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.41,0:16:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, where we barbecued\Nand played watermelon-splitting!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.04,0:16:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the one!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.04,0:16:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Brown went out and fetched some honey...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.25,0:16:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and he brought a swarm of bees along with him...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.43,0:16:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and for some reason the bees only came after me,\Nand my face got all swollen...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.15,0:16:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Take that! Haah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.53,0:16:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoo, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.70,0:16:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind if I play too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.20,0:16:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,James looks kinda down...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.29,0:17:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just upset because of the broken eggs\Nspoiling his Monthly Beauty magazine, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.42,0:17:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't just be that, right? He's depressed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.21,0:17:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh, you beat me again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.21,0:17:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you so good at this, Brown?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.38,0:17:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Now hold on! That one doesn't count!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.64,0:17:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't either of you worried\Nabout James in the slightest?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.40,0:17:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not fun seeing him like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.82,0:17:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.65,0:17:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know why he's depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.66,0:17:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's try to make him smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.83,0:17:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,James!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.79,0:17:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.79,0:17:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know what happened to you,\Nbut you've looked out of it this wholet ime!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.09,0:17:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.54,0:17:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Terrible things keep happening to me,\Nso I don't really feel like smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.96,0:17:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But putting on that gloomy face burdens us too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.51,0:17:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're going to force you to smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.39,0:17:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.86,0:18:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.32,0:18:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You ruined my naturally handsome face!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.03,0:18:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do I have to put up with all this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.65,0:18:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodness me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.61,0:18:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you laughing at?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.28,0:18:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're smiling even though you're angry...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.24,0:18:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's your doing, you know that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.79,0:18:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like my grandmother once said:
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.71,0:18:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,"Good things come to those who smile,\Neven when you're sad."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,How am I supposed to do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.25,0:18:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Just forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.59,0:18:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,They just don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.84,0:18:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't even try to sympathize with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.01,0:18:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And I can't get this tape off, ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.52,0:18:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Monthly Beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.56,0:18:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The same one that got ruined by the eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.03,0:18:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's your change, $4.20!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.91,0:18:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming in!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.62,0:19:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all so different from earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.12,0:19:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it because I was smiling...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.34,0:19:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,James!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.21,0:19:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Sally!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.01,0:19:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Look down, you might've stepped on that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.30,0:19:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.64,0:19:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If you had stepped on that,\Nit would've ruined your smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.60,0:19:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,My smile?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.60,0:19:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. Sally!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.18,0:19:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I called your name in the park earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.94,0:19:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, really? When?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.77,0:19:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.57,0:19:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,How strange, that I didn't notice\Nyour lovely smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.19,0:19:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Lovely smile?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.40,0:19:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.36,0:19:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I know a photographer for a fashion magazine\Nwho's looking for a model,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.45,0:19:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'll be sure to recommend you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.16,0:19:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, a fashion magazine?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.70,0:19:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You might know them! They're called Monthly Beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.66,0:19:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Monthly Beauty you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.79,0:19:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.83,0:19:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, that's the one! You read it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.50,0:19:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I buy it every month!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.55,0:19:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I could model for Monthly Beauty...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.84,0:20:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.97,0:20:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be sure to get your name in!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.43,0:20:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Good smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.48,0:20:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,My, oh, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.44,0:20:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,My smile, forced together with adhesive tape...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.03,0:20:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,is a good smile?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.86,0:20:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like my grandmother once said:
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.99,0:20:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,450)}"Good things come to those who smile,\Neven when they're sad."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true what Moon's grandmother said?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.25,0:20:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.92,0:20:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.59,0:20:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.26,0:20:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Forcing a smile...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.22,0:20:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't going to make Red come back,\Nor clean my room for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.65,0:20:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.82,0:20:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Red!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.86,0:21:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Jessica, is it true?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.82,0:21:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Had a feeling this was yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.24,0:21:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It was abandoned at the train station.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.66,0:21:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It was stolen last week,\Nand I thought I'd never see it again...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.08,0:21:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.13,0:21:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so so much, Jessica!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.09,0:21:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how James is doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.68,0:21:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably took a foot bath and went to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.10,0:21:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.27,0:21:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.86,0:21:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And you look oddly happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.16,0:21:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I bought eggs!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.12,0:21:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.58,0:21:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we can have a real omelette and rice party!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.46,0:21:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But we already ate the ketchup and rice...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.79,0:21:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'll have an omelette party!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.46,0:22:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,– Yummy!\N– It's so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.59,0:22:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This is very good, Cony!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.30,0:22:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.34,0:22:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.35,0:22:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Get this: I might be in the next issue of Monthly Beauty!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.31,0:22:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, how?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.39,0:22:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.18,0:22:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.69,0:22:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.23,0:22:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you all so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.36,0:22:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.32,0:22:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.94,0:22:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Brown, don't drop your plate!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.67,0:24:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Next time on {\i1}Line Town...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.33,0:24:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Cony's childhood friend Michele\Nis coming to Line Town?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.92,0:24:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Huh? Michele is a hottie?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.59,0:24:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Is he really? Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.18,0:24:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}If he's not hot, I won't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.39,0:24:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oh, forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.80,0:24:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Next episode is called "Hottie!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.10,0:24:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}...I mean, "Reunion!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.81,0:24:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tune in next time!
